<div class="p-6 sm:px-20 bg-white border-b border-gray-200">

    <div class="mt-8 text-2xl">
        Welcome to MentalConnect
    </div>

    <div class="mt-6 text-gray-500">
        With MentalConnect you can meet & connect with other people who have a shared interest. <a href="/user/profile">Set up your profile</a> with information about who you are and find others with similar interests. With MentalConnect you can chat with people in our chatbox.
    </div>
</div>

<div class="bg-gray-200 bg-opacity-25 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2">
    <div class="p-6">
        <div class="flex items-center">
        <div class="ml-1 text-indigo-500 text-2xl"><i class="far fa-user-circle"></i></div>
        <div class="ml-4 text-lg leading-7 font-semibold"><a href="/user/profile" class="text-gray-600">Your profile</a></div>
        </div>

        <div class="ml-12">
            <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500">
                <b>Tell others something about yourself so they can get to know you a bit. </b> Information on your profile will be matched with information of other profiles so you can see other people with shared interests.
            </div>

            <a href="/user/profile">
                <div class="mt-3 flex items-center text-sm font-semibold text-indigo-700">
                        <div>Go to your profile</div>

                        <div class="ml-1 text-indigo-500">
                            <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 3.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
                        </div>
                </div>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="p-6 border-t border-gray-200 md:border-t-0 md:border-l">
        <div class="flex items-center">
        <div class="ml-1 text-indigo-500 text-2xl"><i class="far fa-comments"></i></div>
        <div class="ml-4 text-lg leading-7 font-semibold"><a href="https://laracasts.com" class="text-gray-600">Chat with other people</a></div>
        </div>

        <div class="ml-12">
            <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500">
            Participate with one or more people in a real-time conversation as a series of short text exchanges as instant messaging, or by using images, voice, video, or some combination of these.
            </div>

            <a href="https://laracasts.com">
                <div class="mt-3 flex items-center text-sm font-semibold text-indigo-700">
                        <div>Start a chat session</div>

                        <div class="ml-1 text-indigo-500">
                            <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 3.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
                        </div>
                </div>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="p-6 border-t border-gray-200">
        <div class="flex items-center">
        <div class="ml-1 text-indigo-500 text-2xl"><i class="fas fa-satellite-dish"></i></div>
            <div class="ml-4 text-lg leading-7 font-semibold"><a href="https://tailwindcss.com/" class="text-gray-600">Spaces</a></div>
        </div>

        <div class="ml-12">
            <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500">
                Share interest with other people about a specific subject. You can create or join a space about a subject you have a interst in to receive notifiactions about activity within this space.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="p-6 border-t border-gray-200 md:border-l">
        <div class="flex items-center">
        <div class="ml-1 text-indigo-500 text-2xl"><i class="fas fa-photo-video"></i></div>
            <div class="ml-4 text-lg text-gray-600 leading-7 font-semibold">Media</div>
        </div>

        <div class="ml-12">
            <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500">
                View & organize all your shared media 
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
